author: Colin Gleeson
title: Winner of €9.8m jackpot makes contact with National Lottery
description: Winning ticket was sold at Daly’s Supervalu store in Killarney
content:
The holder of the winning ticket of last Saturdays 9.8 million Lotto jackpot has made contact with the National Lottery on Thursday.
